OL,3,C'They were heroes': The Teesside
OL,4,Cvolunteers who fought in the Spanish
OL,5,CCivil War
OL,7,FAn event to remember thirty Teesside
OL,8,Fvolunteers who fought against fascism
OL,9,Fin the Spanish Civil War has been held
OL,10,Fin Hartlepool for the first time.
OL,12,FThe Spanish Civil War arose in the
OL,13,F1930s when right-wing General
OL,14,FFrancisco Franco led a rebel military
OL,15,Fcoup against Spain's democratically
OL,16,Felected government.
