OL,3,C'They were heroes': The Teesside
OL,4,Cvolunteers who fought in the Spanish
OL,5,CCivil War
OL,7,FElaine Spybe's father, Herbert,
OL,8,Ftravelled to Spain from Middlesbrough
OL,9,Fin the 1930's.
OL,11,FShe said: "He hitchhiked, borrowing an
OL,12,Fover coat from his brother, down to
OL,13,FSouthampton and got a cattle train
OL,14,Facross France and hiked over the
OL,15,FPyrenees with other international
OL,16,Fbrigades.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
