OL,3,C'They were heroes': The Teesside
OL,4,Cvolunteers who fought in the Spanish
OL,5,CCivil War
OL,7,F"I think he was a hero. It's at the
OL,8,Fcore of who we are in terms of our
OL,9,Fbeliefs and the importance of
OL,10,Fmaintaining democracy and standing up
OL,11,Ffor what's correct."
OL,13,FOtto Esatensen from Redcar also joined
OL,14,Fthe global movement - the
OL,15,FInternational Brigade to fight against
OL,16,FGeneral Franco's forces.
