OL,3,C'They were heroes': The Teesside
OL,4,Cvolunteers who fought in the Spanish
OL,5,CCivil War
OL,7,FHis nephew John Sutherland said: "Its
OL,8,Fnice to remember these things. It is
OL,9,Fkind of un heard of isn't it because
OL,10,Fbecause the Second World War came so
OL,11,Fquickly after it.
OL,13,F"There's very little said about the
OL,14,FSpanish Civil War unless you're
OL,15,Finterested in that type of history."
OL,17,FTony Fox, from Stockton, helped to
OL,18,Forganise the Hartlepool event today.
